description:
When you are stuck in negativity and destructive emotions you can break out of them using principles coming from Psychology, Chinese Medicine, Kung Fu, Tai Chi and Yoga.

  1. Reduce and remove anxiety and fear..
  2. empower and take charge of your life
  3. Increase your personal contact to unconditional love.

In the course you will learn theory and concepts:

  1. You learn about Energy.
  2. The principles of returning to source.
  3. How to treat difficult problems
  4. Find a new connection to self-love and self healing
title: Delete Pain - Wickes Way
